snippet.title: Café International for iPhone and iPad - Trailer
snippet.description: The all-time classic board game Café International (Game of the Year 1989!) is finally available to your iPhone, iPod and iPad. Enjoy an incredibly addictive gameplay, either alone in two challenging solitary modes, or as multiplayer game against friends and computer players. The unique funny original graphics (of course fully supporting iPad retina) and an awesome gameplay and handling will provide a great atmosphere and countless hours of fun and challenges.
